claim.claim-text:
20. A surgical tray comprising:
a sterile surgical tray prepackaged with a plurality of instruments;
an infusion device held in the sterile surgical tray and operably coupled to at least one of the instruments;
an aspiration device held in the sterile surgical tray and operably coupled to at least one of the instruments;
a processing unit in the sterile surgical tray for controlling at least one of the instruments, the infusion device, and the aspiration device;
wherein at least one of the instruments includes a user control operably coupled to the processing unit for controlling the instrument with the user control and at least one other instrument; and
user feedback devices on the sterile surgical tray and coupled to the processing unit for indicating a current parameter or status information of at least one of the instruments, the infusion device, and the aspiration device.
